h4. Problem Description
If we specify the release versioning as plan variable won't work if the deployment is triggered by scheduled build. It will work if we run the build manually, however somehow on the scheduled job, the variable's value won't get replaced. Instead it will just print out how the variable is specified.

Please refer to the screenshot below.
