# Create a test plan
# Specify Variables inside of the plan for the deployment versioning
{panel}!deploy2.png|width=650!{panel}
# Create a deployment project
# Create a trigger that will auto deployed upon completion of a build
# Configure release versioning and include the variable inside the release version
{panel}!deploy3.png|width=650!{panel}
# Create a trigger for that plan for example a scheduled build
# Wait until the plan is built and the deployment is finished deploying
{panel}!deploy4.png|width=650!{panel}
# Notice the difference with manual build
{panel}!deploy5.png|width=650!{panel}

When a Branch is deleted from the Git repository before the expire time set on the Automatically Manage Branches menu and the Branch Plan is still run by Bamboo but an error is given on the error logs:

{quote}
Plan 'TESTPLAN20' could not be started. Exception: com.atlassian.bamboo.repository.InvalidRepositoryException: Cannot determine head revision of 'https://github.com/example/example.git' on branch  'example/branch'. Branch has probably been removed.

Plan 'TESTPLAN20' detected that the repository is invalid. The plan will be disabled.
{quote}

That branch is then disabled but remains on the branch list indefinitely. Bamboo should remove that Branch from the list as the branch does no longer exists.

h4. Problem Description
Some of the variables do not work in Bamboo despite it's documented in [Bamboo Variables|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/BAMBOO/Bamboo+variables]. Here are some of the variables that do not work.
{noformat}
bamboo.shortPlanKey
bamboo.shortPlanName
{noformat}

It will return something similar like the following error message.
{noformat}
/tmp/TPRO-PG-JOB1-35-ScriptBuildTask-2385598182076022059.sh: 2: /tmp/TPRO-PG-JOB1-35-ScriptBuildTask-2385598182076022059.sh: Bad substitution
{noformat}
h4. Steps to replicate
# Create a test Plan
# Create a script task in that plan, leave everything on default will do
# Put the following on the script text box
{noformat}
echo ${bamboo.shortPlanKey}
echo ${bamboo.shortPlanName}
{noformat}
